The paper focuses on 3D face alignment using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of attention mechanisms and loss functions also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of data enhancement methods and virtual pose face data sets suggests a focus on multimedia (cs.MM) and graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories.
